# Ranking Functions Comparison

| Feature | ROW_NUMBER() | RANK() | DENSE_RANK() |
|----------|--------------|---------|--------------|
|Duplicates share rank?|❌|✅|✅|
|Ranking gaps?|❌|✅|❌|
|Every row unique?|✅|❌|❌|
|Top K Distinct?|❌|⚠️|✅|
|Leaderboard?|❌|✅|✅|
|LeetCode favorite?|Medium|Medium|★★★★★|

---

