Input

```text
100

100

90

80

80

70
```

ROW_NUMBER()

```text
100 → 1

100 → 2

90 → 3

80 → 4

80 → 5

70 → 6
```

---

RANK()

```text
100 → 1

100 → 1

90 → 3

80 → 4

80 → 4

70 → 6
```

---

