# Common Mistakes

## Mistake 1

Using

```sql
GROUP BY
```

instead of

```sql
OVER()
```

Result

Rows disappear.

---

## Mistake 2

Using

```sql
ROW_NUMBER()
```

for Top K.

Fails duplicate tests.

---

## Mistake 3

Ignoring duplicates.

Interviewers intentionally include duplicate salaries.

---

## Mistake 4

Using

```sql
LIMIT
```

inside grouped ranking questions.

Returns Top K globally.

Not

Top K per department.

---

## Mistake 5

Forgetting

```sql
PARTITION BY
```

Entire table gets ranked.

Department ranking becomes incorrect.

---

## Mistake 6

Using

```sql
RANGE
```

when question asks

Previous K rows.

Should be

```sql
ROWS
```

---

## Mistake 7

Skipping

daily aggregation

before moving averages.

Multiple transactions per day produce incorrect windows.

