# Window Functions vs GROUP BY

| Feature | GROUP BY | Window Function |
|----------|----------|-----------------|
|Keeps all rows?|❌|✅|
|Ranking?|❌|✅|
|Running total?|❌|✅|
|Moving average?|❌|✅|
|Top K per group?|⚠️ Difficult|✅|
|Previous row?|❌|✅|
|Next row?|❌|✅|

