# SQL Execution Order

One of the most common interview follow-up questions.

Logical order

```text
FROM

↓

WHERE

↓

GROUP BY

↓

HAVING

↓

WINDOW FUNCTIONS

↓

SELECT

↓

ORDER BY

↓

LIMIT
```

Important implication

Window functions

cannot be used

inside

```sql
WHERE
```

Wrong

```sql
SELECT *

FROM Employee

WHERE

DENSE_RANK()

OVER(

ORDER BY salary DESC

)=1;
```

Correct

```sql
WITH Ranked AS
(
SELECT *,

DENSE_RANK()

OVER(

ORDER BY salary DESC

) AS r

FROM Employee
)

SELECT *

FROM Ranked

WHERE r=1;
```

